Nicola McLean hits Kim Woodburn with brutal 'baby' slur after star's heartbreaking stillborn burial confession The housemates clash as things heat up after nominations for this week's eviction Share Click to play Tap to play The video will start in 8 Cancel Play now Nicola Mclean loses her temper when Kim calls her a liar Share this video Get celebs   Thank you for subscribing!   
Nicola McLean insists she can "go lower" as her feud with Kim Woodburn becomes heated and very personal on Celebrity Big Brother . 
The star doesn't hold back as the two housemates engaged in a bitter row over this week's nominations, with Kim claiming she told lies about her as she put her up for the vote. 
Nicola confronts her fellow celeb to ask what she's talking about, but Kim refuses to engage in the argument, responding: "I will not rise to your bait." Kim has put Nicola up for eviction (Photo: Channel 5) The pair clash once again (Photo: Channel 5) Does Nicola go too low with this? (Photo: Channel 5) 
As the row continues, the How Clean Is Your House? star fires back: "Grow up, you're a mum." Read More 
However, Nicola says: "And you're not, that's your problem. If you want to go low, I'll go lower." She insists Nicola told lies about her (Photo: Channel 5) Do the comments hit too close to home?
